name: DBZ Saiyan Son Goku
text:
When this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Kamehameha" Spell/Trap Card from Deck to your hand. This card must be face-up on the field to activate and resolve this effect.
Once per turn, you can move this card to an unused adjecent Main Monster Zone.
